{"id": 3027, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得什么样才叫做“会花钱”？", "description": "或者说，你觉得所谓的“财务成熟”应该是一种啥样的状态？（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 1534, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191013225433DvBgas73Z5RcXFyS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-13T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 348429, "content": "买自己喜欢并且你确实回会用得到，同时经常用的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1658146}, {"id": 348449, "content": "不会头脑发热，明白收支与需求", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632590}, {"id": 348718, "content": "嫖娼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659094}, {"id": 348241, "content": "用“值不值得”而不是简单的“贵不贵”来衡量一项消费/支出", "image": null, "praise_count": 477, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348242, "content": "很少会后悔“咋囤了这么多不需要的东西”", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348243, "content": "帮自己存了一份“哪天不爽就随时走人”基金", "image": null, "praise_count": 265, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348244, "content": "购物时，不会出现“等冷静下来时钱已经付出去了”的时刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 86, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 348248, "content": "我的角度是花的我自己很开心（长期），别人的角度是这钱花的让我很舒服🌝", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 348254, "content": "承包整个村的鱼塘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492793}, {"id": 348255, "content": "承包鱼塘", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492793}, {"id": 348256, "content": "少吃或不吃深加工食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044540}, {"id": 348257, "content": "如果卖的东西用不到，挺肥钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998568}, {"id": 348258, "content": "对广告商有辨别力，不掉入消费主义的陷阱", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224557}, {"id": 348259, "content": "只选对的，不选贵的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 348260, "content": "识辨欲望与真正所需\n明白每一笔花费的用处", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 348261, "content": "想好了再买，不要问性价比，问值不值得。买了就好好用，用的开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1583360}, {"id": 348262, "content": "现在不懂花钱，进来学习！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347494}, {"id": 348263, "content": "与时间成本、健康成本匹配的蹲来的优惠金额", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278658}, {"id": 348264, "content": "购买时得到的满足和使用时得到的满足足以抵消为此付出的损失", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666683}, {"id": 348265, "content": "产出比投入多的投资", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400615}, {"id": 348266, "content": "学会以小资本抵御大风险\n消费前先想想我需不需要", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661463}, {"id": 348267, "content": "明白值得与不值得 不被表象迷惑买不适合消费阶级的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1487006}, {"id": 348268, "content": "可买可不买的东西都不买，「万一用得上」就等于用不上，警惕一切消费升级。否则永远攒不下第一桶金，连裸辞都不敢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497766}, {"id": 348269, "content": "意识到有能力去购买一样东西并不等同于为此努力攒了很长时间钱只为去购买它。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 348271, "content": "为自己的未来买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664534}, {"id": 348272, "content": "1.为自己的需求消费，而不是为别人。\n2.一分钱一分货，这个道理永恒不变。\n3.选择包装和宣传比较诚实的商品。\n4.如果有早餐店用纸包装而不是塑料袋，这样的店活该生意兴隆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649440}, {"id": 348273, "content": "只买自己最喜欢的，不将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657731}, {"id": 348274, "content": "按需购买", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680527}, {"id": 348276, "content": "当“财务”有机会实现“自由”的时候，懂得选择自由而不是继续追逐更大的“财务”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118083}, {"id": 348277, "content": "能做到绝大部分自由，买开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570237}, {"id": 348279, "content": "果断买下来的东西，后来都涨价了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107631}, {"id": 348280, "content": "十年以后还觉得值", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665704}, {"id": 348281, "content": "不盲目消费，跟风买所谓的潮流品，能存下一笔钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 348282, "content": "买贵的，可以用很久，值得。货比三家性价比可能更好，但花的时间成本算上，根本不划算。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110005}, {"id": 348284, "content": "有钱花在刀背上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238342}, {"id": 348285, "content": "买来都能确实用到不会放在那里积灰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775953}, {"id": 348287, "content": "不会后悔，但是我经常，所以现在少买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661387}, {"id": 348288, "content": "当真正穷过一次之后，就学会花钱了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451284}, {"id": 348289, "content": "买房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066439}, {"id": 349057, "content": "以上都是我，但我还是穷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618604}, {"id": 348290, "content": "对自己产生的价值超过80%", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1439083}, {"id": 348291, "content": "投资自己，投资家人，投资健康和未来。合理支出，不负债消费。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666781}, {"id": 348293, "content": "没有抖音 不买网红", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661800}, {"id": 348294, "content": "自己觉得值，就算", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002376}, {"id": 348295, "content": "理性与虚荣心达到一个平衡点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290000}, {"id": 348296, "content": "大家开心了才叫会花钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203616}, {"id": 348299, "content": "我自己是，想买一个东西，先冷一个星期，如果还有要买的必要和热情就拍下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370362}, {"id": 348300, "content": "当下来看，只买需要的东西；长远来讲，财务成熟代表着你需要一张存折了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666811}, {"id": 348302, "content": "借钱的时候能做好收不回的准备", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103045}, {"id": 348309, "content": "每次钱只花一半！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666833}]}